<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>FortuneTab 심층 리포트 — {{ user.name }}</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;800;900&family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  /* ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     FortuneTab 심층 리포트 · v2 "New Eastern Editorial"
     플래너 디자인 언어와 통일: 미색 종이 + 먹선 + Playfair 거대 숫자
     + 세로 한자 + 낙관 · A4 세로 5 섹션
     ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  :root {
    --paper:       #faf6ee;   /* 미색 종이 */
    --ink:         #1a1814;   /* 먹 */
    --ink-faint:   #8b857a;   /* 옅은 먹 */
    --ink-softer:  #bcb5a6;   /* 더 옅은 선 */
    --seal:        #b8322a;   /* 낙관 적갈색 */
    --accent:      #1a2a6c;   /* 테마 accent (navy 기본) */
    --accent-deep: #0f1a4a;
    --gold:        #b8860b;   /* 용신 표시 */
    --faint-bg:    #f4eee0;   /* 미색 조금 진한 배경 */
    --serif:       "Noto Serif KR", "Nanum Myeongjo", serif;
    --playfair:    "Playfair Display", "Noto Serif KR", serif;
  }

  @page {
    size: A4 portrait;
    margin: 20mm 16mm 22mm 16mm;
    background: var(--paper);
    @bottom-center {
      content: "FORTUNETAB · " counter(page) " / " counter(pages);
      font-family: var(--playfair);
      font-size: 8.5pt;
      letter-spacing: 2pt;
      color: var(--ink-faint);
    }
  }
  @page cover {
    margin: 0;
    @bottom-center { content: ""; }
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }
  html, body {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 10.5pt;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.72;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: var(--paper);
  }

  /* ─── 공통 타이포 ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  h1, h2, h3, h4 { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 6pt; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--playfair); font-size: 28pt; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.2pt; }
  h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 18pt; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 14pt; }
  h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 11.5pt; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-top: 16pt; letter-spacing: 0.3pt; }
  p  { margin: 0 0 8pt; }

  b, strong { font-weight: 700; }
  .muted { color: var(--ink-faint); }
  .gold  { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
  .seal  { color: var(--seal); font-weight: 700; }
  .hanja { color: var(--ink-faint); font-size: 0.9em; font-family: var(--serif); }

  /* 페이지 분리 */
  .page-break { page-break-before: always; }

  /* 상단 머리글 (표지 이외 모든 섹션 공통) */
  .page-head {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 3pt;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    border-bottom: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    padding-bottom: 5pt;
    margin-bottom: 16pt;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .page-head .mark {
    display: inline-block; width: 5pt; height: 5pt; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent); margin-right: 4pt;
    vertical-align: middle; transform: translateY(-1pt);
  }

  /* ─── 섹션 헤더 (플래너 drawSectionHeadV2 대응) ──────────────────── */
  .section-head {
    display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 14pt;
    margin-bottom: 16pt;
  }
  .section-head .num {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 40pt; font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 0.9;
  }
  .section-head .en {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 4pt; color: var(--ink-faint);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: block;
  }
  .section-head .ko {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 17pt; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: block;
    margin-top: 2pt;
  }
  .section-head .labels { padding-top: 6pt; }
  .section-divider {
    height: 0.9pt; background: var(--ink);
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin: 0 0 22pt;
  }

  /* ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     COVER — 미색 종이 + 좌측 세로 한자 + 우측 거대 연도 + 중앙 제목 + 낙관
     ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  section.cover {
    page: cover;
    page-break-after: always;
    height: 297mm; width: 210mm;
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: 22mm 18mm;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cover .head {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 4pt;
    color: var(--ink-faint); text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
    border-bottom: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    padding-bottom: 6mm;
  }
  .cover .head .right { color: var(--seal); }
  .cover .kanji-col {
    position: absolute; left: 22mm; top: 60mm;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 46pt; font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--accent-deep); opacity: 0.82;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .cover .kanji-col span { display: block; }
  .cover .kanji-rule {
    position: absolute; left: 40mm; top: 62mm; bottom: 60mm;
    width: 0.7pt; background: var(--accent); opacity: 0.3;
  }
  .cover .year {
    position: absolute; right: 18mm; top: 76mm;
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 168pt; font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--accent); opacity: 0.95;
    line-height: 0.9; letter-spacing: -3pt;
  }
  .cover .year-gz {
    position: absolute; right: 18mm; top: 164mm;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 16pt; color: var(--ink); opacity: 0.72;
  }
  .cover .year-rule {
    position: absolute; right: 18mm; top: 158mm;
    width: 74mm; height: 0.6pt;
    background: var(--ink); opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .cover .title-block {
    position: absolute; left: 18mm; right: 18mm;
    top: 188mm; text-align: center;
  }
  .cover .title-block .main {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 34pt; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.5pt;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .cover .title-block .main .name {
    color: var(--seal);
  }
  .cover .title-block .dot {
    display: inline-block; width: 4pt; height: 4pt; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent); margin: 8pt auto;
  }
  .cover .title-block .sub {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-top: 8pt;
  }
  .cover .title-block .en {
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif KR", serif;
    font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 11pt; color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-top: 4pt;
  }
  .cover .meta {
    position: absolute; bottom: 30mm; left: 18mm; right: 58mm;
    border-top: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    padding-top: 6mm;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 9.5pt; color: var(--ink-faint);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 6mm;
  }
  .cover .meta .k { font-size: 8pt; letter-spacing: 1.5pt; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 2pt; }
  .cover .meta .v { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }
  .cover .seal {
    position: absolute; right: 18mm; bottom: 26mm;
    width: 24mm; height: 24mm;
    background: var(--seal);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1.2pt #fff8f0;
  }
  .cover .seal .ch {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 36pt; font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff8f0;
  }
  .cover .disclaimer {
    position: absolute; bottom: 10mm; left: 18mm; right: 18mm;
    font-size: 7.5pt; color: var(--ink-faint);
    text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.3pt;
  }

  /* ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     01 — 핵심 통찰
     ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .oneliner {
    background: var(--faint-bg);
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    border-left: 3pt solid var(--seal);
    padding: 14pt 18pt;
    margin: 0 0 18pt;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 13pt;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .oneliner .quote-mark {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 22pt; color: var(--seal);
    opacity: 0.55;
    display: block; margin-bottom: -4pt;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .insight-card {
    display: flex; gap: 10pt;
    padding: 11pt 14pt;
    margin-bottom: 7pt;
    border-bottom: 0.4pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .insight-card:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .insight-card .idx {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 22pt; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent); min-width: 26pt;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .insight-card .body .t { font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 3pt; font-size: 11pt; }
  .insight-card .body .b { font-size: 10pt; color: #3d3833; line-height: 1.65; }

  .watchout-group { margin-top: 10pt; }
  .watchout {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    border-left: 2.5pt solid var(--seal);
    padding: 9pt 14pt; margin-top: 6pt;
    font-size: 10pt;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .watchout .area { font-weight: 700; color: var(--seal); margin-right: 4pt; }

  /* ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     02 — 사주 구조
     ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .pillars {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 6pt; margin-bottom: 16pt;
  }
  .pillars .pillar {
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: 10pt 6pt 12pt;
    text-align: center;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .pillars .pillar .ph {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 8pt; letter-spacing: 2pt;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 6pt;
  }
  .pillars .pillar .hj {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 26pt; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .pillars .pillar .ko {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 9pt; color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-top: 3pt;
  }
  .pillars .pillar .el {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 8.5pt; letter-spacing: 1.5pt;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-top: 5pt;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .kv-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0; margin-bottom: 12pt;
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
  }
  .kv-grid .kv {
    padding: 9pt 12pt;
    border-right: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
  }
  .kv-grid .kv:last-child { border-right: 0; }
  .kv-grid .kv .k {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 8pt; letter-spacing: 1.5pt;
    color: var(--ink-faint); text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 3pt;
  }
  .kv-grid .kv .v {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .elements-bar {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 6pt; margin: 6pt 0 14pt;
  }
  .elements-bar .el-cell {
    text-align: center;
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .elements-bar .el-cell .num {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 22pt; font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10pt 0 8pt;
  }
  .elements-bar .el-cell .name {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 9pt; color: var(--ink);
    padding: 5pt 0;
    background: var(--paper);
    border-top: 0.4pt solid var(--ink-softer);
  }
  .el-wood  .num { background: #3f6e3a; }
  .el-fire  .num { background: #a8372a; }
  .el-earth .num { background: #8a6434; }
  .el-metal .num { background: #8a8a8a; }
  .el-water .num { background: #2a3e6a; }

  ul.keylist {
    padding-left: 14pt; margin: 4pt 0 10pt;
    list-style: none;
  }
  ul.keylist li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 12pt;
    margin-bottom: 5pt;
    font-size: 10pt;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  ul.keylist li::before {
    content: "·"; color: var(--seal);
    font-weight: 900; font-size: 14pt;
    position: absolute; left: 0; top: -4pt;
  }

  .narrative {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    padding: 13pt 16pt;
    margin-top: 6pt;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--ink);
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }

  /* ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     03 — 연간 · 대운
     ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .daeun-box {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    padding: 14pt 16pt; margin-bottom: 11pt;
    position: relative;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .daeun-box::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 3pt; height: 100%;
    background: var(--accent);
  }
  .daeun-box.next::before { background: var(--gold); }
  .daeun-box .period {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 11.5pt; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 3pt;
  }
  .daeun-box.next .period { color: var(--gold); }
  .daeun-box .theme {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 10.5pt; color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 8pt;
  }

  .quarter-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 4pt; margin: 6pt 0 12pt;
  }
  .quarter-grid .q {
    padding: 9pt 10pt; vertical-align: top;
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    background: var(--paper);
    font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 1.55;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .quarter-grid .q .qlabel {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 8.5pt; letter-spacing: 1.5pt;
    color: var(--seal);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 4pt; font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     04 — 월별 세운 (카드 그리드)
     ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .month-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 8pt 10pt;
  }
  .month-card {
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: 10pt 12pt;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
    position: relative;
  }
  .month-card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 2.5pt; height: 100%;
    background: var(--accent); opacity: 0.55;
  }
  .month-card .head {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 5pt;
  }
  .month-card .num {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 20pt; font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent); line-height: 1;
  }
  .month-card .pillar {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 9pt; color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
  .month-card .keyword {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 0.5pt solid var(--seal);
    color: var(--seal);
    padding: 1.5pt 6pt;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 5pt;
  }
  .month-card .energy {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 10pt; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 4pt;
  }
  .month-card .focus,
  .month-card .watch {
    font-size: 9pt; color: #3d3833;
    margin-bottom: 2pt;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .month-card .watch { color: var(--seal); }

  /* ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     05 — 행동 가이드 GROW 4법
     ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .grow-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 6pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;
  }
  .grow-cell {
    padding: 12pt 14pt;
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    background: var(--paper);
    page-break-inside: avoid;
    position: relative;
  }
  .grow-cell .gtag {
    position: absolute; top: -7pt; left: 12pt;
    background: var(--paper);
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--seal);
    padding: 0 6pt;
    letter-spacing: 4pt;
  }
  .grow-cell .title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink);
    margin: 3pt 0 7pt;
    font-size: 11pt;
  }

  .first-sprout {
    background: var(--faint-bg);
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--gold);
    padding: 16pt 18pt; margin-top: 14pt;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .first-sprout .label {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 3pt;
    color: var(--seal);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 4pt;
  }
  .first-sprout .body {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 11.5pt; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .weekly-habits {
    margin-top: 12pt;
    border: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    background: var(--paper);
  }
  .weekly-habits .row {
    display: flex; gap: 14pt;
    padding: 7pt 14pt;
    border-bottom: 0.4pt dotted var(--ink-softer);
    font-size: 10pt;
  }
  .weekly-habits .row:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .weekly-habits .day {
    font-family: var(--playfair);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
    min-width: 32pt;
    letter-spacing: 1pt;
  }

  /* ─── 푸터 면책 ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .foot-disclaimer {
    margin-top: 20pt; padding-top: 10pt;
    border-top: 0.6pt solid var(--ink-softer);
    font-size: 8pt; color: var(--ink-faint);
    text-align: center; line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.3pt;
  }

</style>
</head>
<body>

{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   PAGE 1 — 커버
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="cover">
  <div class="head">
    <span>FORTUNETAB</span>
    <span class="right">EST · MMXXVI</span>
  </div>

  <div class="kanji-col">
    <span>運</span><span>命</span><span>流</span>
  </div>
  <div class="kanji-rule"></div>

  <div class="year">{{ meta.current_year }}</div>
  <div class="year-rule"></div>
  <div class="year-gz">심층 리포트 · DEEP READING</div>

  <div class="title-block">
    <div class="main"><span class="name">{{ user.name }}</span>님의 운명 흐름</div>
    <div class="dot"></div>
    <div class="sub">Where Eastern Wisdom Meets Western Stars</div>
    <div class="en">A yearly reading of destiny, crafted for one person only.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="meta">
    <div>
      <div class="k">Order</div>
      <div class="v">{{ order_number }}</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="k">Issued</div>
      <div class="v">{{ meta.issued_at }}</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="k">Birth</div>
      <div class="v">{{ user.birth_date }} · {{ user.birth_time }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="seal"><span class="ch">命</span></div>

  <div class="disclaimer">
    본 분석은 참고 용도이며, 전문 상담이나 의료·법률 결정을 대체하지 않습니다.
  </div>
</section>

{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   PAGE 2 — 핵심 통찰
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section>
  <div class="page-head">
    <span><span class="mark"></span>FORTUNETAB · DEEP READING</span>
    <span>{{ meta.current_year }}</span>
  </div>

  <div class="section-head">
    <div class="num">01</div>
    <div class="labels">
      <span class="en">Insight</span>
      <span class="ko">올해의 한 줄, 그리고 세 가지 통찰</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <div class="oneliner">
    <span class="quote-mark">“</span>
    {{ insight_highlight.one_line }}
  </div>

  {% for it in insight_highlight.top_insights %}
  <div class="insight-card">
    <div class="idx">{{ loop.index | pad2 }}</div>
    <div class="body">
      <div class="t">{{ it.title }}</div>
      <div class="b">{{ it.body }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}

  <h3>주의할 지점</h3>
  <div class="watchout-group">
    {% for w in insight_highlight.watchouts %}
    <div class="watchout">
      <span class="area">{{ w.area }}</span>{{ w.caution }}
      {% if w.timing %}<span class="muted"> · {{ w.timing }}</span>{% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   PAGE 3 — 사주 구조
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="page-break">
  <div class="page-head">
    <span><span class="mark"></span>SAJU · 당신의 원형</span>
    <span>{{ meta.current_year }}</span>
  </div>

  <div class="section-head">
    <div class="num">02</div>
    <div class="labels">
      <span class="en">Saju Structure</span>
      <span class="ko">사주 구조 · 당신의 원형</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <div class="pillars">
    {% for p in [saju_core.four_pillars.year, saju_core.four_pillars.month, saju_core.four_pillars.day, saju_core.four_pillars.hour] %}
      {% set labels = ['Year 年','Month 月','Day 日','Hour 時'] %}
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="ph">{{ labels[loop.index0] }}</div>
        {% if p %}
          <div class="hj">{{ p.hj }}</div>
          <div class="ko">{{ p.ko }}</div>
          <div class="el">{{ p.element }}</div>
        {% else %}
          <div class="hj muted">—</div>
          <div class="ko muted">시간 미입력</div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="kv-grid">
    <div class="kv">
      <div class="k">Day Master · 일간</div>
      <div class="v">{{ saju_core.day_master.stem }} · {{ saju_core.day_master.element }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kv">
      <div class="k">Strength · 일간 강약</div>
      <div class="v">{{ saju_core.day_master.strength }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>오행 분포</h3>
  <div class="elements-bar">
    {% for row in [
      ['wood', '木 · 목', 'el-wood'],
      ['fire', '火 · 화', 'el-fire'],
      ['earth', '土 · 토', 'el-earth'],
      ['metal', '金 · 금', 'el-metal'],
      ['water', '水 · 수', 'el-water']
    ] %}
    <div class="el-cell {{ row[2] }}">
      <span class="num">{{ saju_core.five_elements[row[0]] }}</span>
      <div class="name">{{ row[1] }}</div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="kv-grid">
    <div class="kv">
      <div class="k">Yongsin · 용신</div>
      <div class="v gold">{{ saju_core.yongsin.element }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kv">
      <div class="k">선정 근거</div>
      <div class="v" style="font-size:9.5pt; font-weight:400;">{{ saju_core.yongsin.reason }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% if saju_core.sipsin_highlight %}
  <h3>십신 포인트</h3>
  <ul class="keylist">
    {% for s in saju_core.sipsin_highlight %}
    <li><b>{{ s.position }}</b> · {{ s.name }} — {{ s.meaning }}</li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  {% endif %}

  <h3>일간 해석</h3>
  <div class="narrative">{{ saju_core.day_master.description }}</div>

  <h3>큰 그림</h3>
  <div class="narrative">{{ saju_core.narrative }}</div>
</section>

{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   PAGE 4 — 연간 · 대운
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="page-break">
  <div class="page-head">
    <span><span class="mark"></span>ANNUAL · DAEUN</span>
    <span>{{ meta.current_year }}</span>
  </div>

  <div class="section-head">
    <div class="num">03</div>
    <div class="labels">
      <span class="en">Annual · Daeun</span>
      <span class="ko">{{ meta.current_year }}년 흐름 · 10년 대운</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <div class="daeun-box">
    <div class="period">현재 대운 · {{ annual_outlook.current_daeun.period }} · {{ annual_outlook.current_daeun.pillar_hj }} ({{ annual_outlook.current_daeun.pillar_ko }})</div>
    <div class="theme">{{ annual_outlook.current_daeun.theme }}</div>

    <h3 style="margin-top:10pt;">기회</h3>
    <ul class="keylist">
      {% for o in annual_outlook.current_daeun.opportunities %}<li>{{ o }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ul>

    {% if annual_outlook.current_daeun.challenges %}
    <h3>과제</h3>
    <ul class="keylist">
      {% for c in annual_outlook.current_daeun.challenges %}<li>{{ c }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endif %}

    {% if annual_outlook.current_daeun.transition_signs %}
    <h3>전환의 신호</h3>
    <p style="font-size:10pt;">{{ annual_outlook.current_daeun.transition_signs }}</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  {% if annual_outlook.next_daeun_preview %}
  <div class="daeun-box next">
    <div class="period">다음 대운 예고 · {{ annual_outlook.next_daeun_preview.period }} · {{ annual_outlook.next_daeun_preview.pillar_hj }}</div>
    <div class="theme">{{ annual_outlook.next_daeun_preview.one_line }}</div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <h3 style="margin-top:16pt;">{{ annual_outlook.annual_flow.year }}년 세운 · {{ annual_outlook.annual_flow.seun_pillar }}</h3>
  <p><b class="gold">주제:</b> {{ annual_outlook.annual_flow.theme }}</p>

  <div class="quarter-grid">
    {% for row in [['q1', 'Q1 · 1~3월'], ['q2', 'Q2 · 4~6월'], ['q3', 'Q3 · 7~9월'], ['q4', 'Q4 · 10~12월']] %}
    <div class="q">
      <div class="qlabel">{{ row[1] }}</div>
      <div>{{ annual_outlook.annual_flow.quarters[row[0]] }}</div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  {% if annual_outlook.annual_flow.key_months %}
  <h3>주요 시기</h3>
  <ul class="keylist">
    {% for km in annual_outlook.annual_flow.key_months %}
    <li><b>{{ km.month }}월</b> — {{ km.why }} <span class="muted">(권장: {{ km.action }})</span></li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  {% endif %}

  <h3>내러티브</h3>
  <div class="narrative">{{ annual_outlook.narrative }}</div>
</section>

{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   PAGE 5 — 월별 세운 12개
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="page-break">
  <div class="page-head">
    <span><span class="mark"></span>MONTHLY FLOW</span>
    <span>{{ meta.current_year }}</span>
  </div>

  <div class="section-head">
    <div class="num">04</div>
    <div class="labels">
      <span class="en">Monthly Flow</span>
      <span class="ko">{{ meta.current_year }}년 월별 세운</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <div class="month-grid">
    {% for m in monthly_seun.months %}
    <div class="month-card">
      <div class="head">
        <span class="num">{{ m.month | pad2 }}</span>
        <span class="pillar">{{ m.seun_pillar_ko }}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="keyword">#{{ m.keyword }}</div>
      <div class="energy">{{ m.energy }}</div>
      <div class="focus"><b>집중:</b> {{ m.focus }}</div>
      <div class="watch"><b>주의:</b> {{ m.watch_out }}</div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   PAGE 6 — 행동 가이드 GROW 4법
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="page-break">
  <div class="page-head">
    <span><span class="mark"></span>ACTION · GROW</span>
    <span>{{ meta.current_year }}</span>
  </div>

  <div class="section-head">
    <div class="num">05</div>
    <div class="labels">
      <span class="en">Action · Grow 4</span>
      <span class="ko">실행 가이드 · 첫 싹에서 결실까지</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <div class="grow-grid">
    <div class="grow-cell">
      <span class="gtag">G</span>
      <div class="title">{{ action_guide.grow_four.goal.title }}</div>
      <ul class="keylist">
        {% for i in action_guide.grow_four.goal.items %}<li>{{ i }}</li>{% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="grow-cell">
      <span class="gtag">R</span>
      <div class="title">{{ action_guide.grow_four.reality.title }}</div>
      <ul class="keylist">
        {% for i in action_guide.grow_four.reality.items %}<li>{{ i }}</li>{% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grow-grid">
    <div class="grow-cell">
      <span class="gtag">O</span>
      <div class="title">{{ action_guide.grow_four.options.title }}</div>
      <ul class="keylist">
        {% for i in action_guide.grow_four.options.items %}<li>{{ i }}</li>{% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="grow-cell">
      <span class="gtag">W</span>
      <div class="title">{{ action_guide.grow_four.will.title }}</div>
      <ul class="keylist">
        {% for i in action_guide.grow_four.will.items %}<li>{{ i }}</li>{% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% if action_guide.weekly_habits %}
  <h3>주간 리듬</h3>
  <div class="weekly-habits">
    {% for h in action_guide.weekly_habits %}
    <div class="row"><span class="day">{{ h.day }}</span>{{ h.habit }}</div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <div class="first-sprout">
    <div class="label">FIRST SPROUT · 첫 싹</div>
    <div class="body">{{ action_guide.first_sprout }}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="foot-disclaimer">
    본 분석은 참고 용도이며, 전문 상담이나 의료·법률·재무 의사결정을 대체하지 않습니다.<br>
    © FORTUNETAB · fortunetab.com · 발행 {{ meta.issued_at }}
  </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
